30:["$","div",null,{"className":"mb-10","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6","children":"Frequently Asked Questions"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"space-y-4","children":[["$","div","faq-0",{"className":"bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-xl p-6","children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3","children":"How much does AI call answering cost for UK tradespeople?"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-white/70 leading-relaxed","children":"whoza.ai plans start at £59 per month for the Starter plan, which includes unlimited calls and WhatsApp delivery. The Growth plan at £125 per month adds team features and priority support. All plans include a 7-day free trial with no credit card required."}]]}],["$","div","faq-1",{"className":"bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-xl p-6","children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3","children":"Can AI call answering handle emergency calls?"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-white/70 leading-relaxed","children":"Yes. AI call handlers identify emergency keywords like burst pipe, no power, gas leak, or flooding and flag them immediately in the WhatsApp summary. For genuine emergencies, the AI can patch the call through to you directly or escalate via urgent notification."}]]}],["$","div","faq-2",{"className":"bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-xl p-6","children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3","children":"Do customers know they are talking to AI?"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-white/70 leading-relaxed","children":"Most callers do not realise. Modern AI uses natural language and human-like voice synthesis. If asked directly, the AI responds honestly. Customers care about getting their problem solved quickly, not about who answers the phone."}]]}],["$","div","faq-3",{"className":"bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-xl p-6","children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3","children":"How long does it take to set up AI call answering?"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-white/70 leading-relaxed","children":"Most businesses are live within 30 minutes. You connect your existing phone number via call forwarding, set your business details and preferences, and the AI starts answering immediately. No hardware, no software installation, and no technical knowledge required."}]]}],["$","div","faq-4",{"className":"bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-xl p-6","children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3","children":"Will AI call answering work with my existing phone number?"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-white/70 leading-relaxed","children":"Yes. whoza.ai connects to your existing business landline or mobile number through call forwarding. Your customers dial the same number they always have. The AI simply answers when you cannot."}]]}],["$","div","faq-5",{"className":"bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-xl p-6","children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3","children":"What is the ROI of AI call answering for tradespeople?"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-white/70 leading-relaxed","children":"At £59 per month, one recovered job pays for the entire service. Most tradespeople capture 3-5 extra jobs per month, generating £840-£1,400 in additional monthly revenue. Annual ROI typically exceeds 1,000%."}]]}],["$","div","faq-6",{"className":"bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-xl p-6","children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3","children":"Can AI call answering handle multiple calls at once?"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-white/70 leading-relaxed","children":"Yes. AI call handlers can manage unlimited simultaneous calls. During busy periods or marketing campaigns, every call is answered and qualified. There are no busy signals and no callers left on hold."}]]}],"$L4d"]}]]}]
